{"tid":1433442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來環保團體都有connect埋？ 文宣講埋催淚彈損兒童腦部發展？","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:27:04.000Z","uid":41576,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f39cc22dab912383bc2d51485c7ffa94bbc3567","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"【#本周焦點 - 諮詢就要聽民意】<br />\n<br />\n政府早前正式展開空氣質素指標(AQO)嘅公眾諮詢，但入面嘅修訂建議，只係小修小補。我哋聯同其他環團，組成「空氣質素指標檢討關注組」，早前電話訪問咗574名市民，有一半受訪者都反對今次嘅修訂，更加有超過7成受訪者不滿政府大幅放寬微細懸浮粒子PM2.5嘅可容許超標次數！空氣質素關乎市民健康，政府必需要聆聽民意，訂立更進取嘅修訂指標！<br />\n<br />\n#我要清新空氣 #CleanAirNow<br />\n---------------------------------------------<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/13716140500/posts/10161986916235501?s=100004559563385&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F13716140500%2Fposts%2F10161986916235501%3Fs%3D100004559563385%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=62858670\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/13716140500/posts/10161986916235501?s=100004559563385&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n空氣污染指數損兒童腦部發展或增抑鬱症狀率<br />\n<br />\n【#本周焦點 - 可怕的路邊空氣污染】<br />\n<br />\n小朋友健康快樂咁成長，應該係各位家長嘅最大心願。但面對空氣污染，小朋友嘅健康備受威脅，美國有研究發現，路邊空氣污染物會損害兒童嘅腦部發展，更加可能增加患上抑鬱症狀嘅機率！為咗小朋友嘅身體，大家要努力發聲，要求政府處理空氣污染問題！<br />\n<br />\n#我要清新空氣 #CleanAirNow #SweepOutNO2<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/13716140500/posts/10161990804950501?s=100004559563385&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F13716140500%2Fposts%2F10161990804950501%3Fs%3D100004559563385%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=119395ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/13716140500/posts/10161990804950501?s=100004559563385&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n聽天文台講最近空氣污染指數爆登 <br />\n<br />\n班狗總共發咗1000+800發催淚彈 天水圍仲要喺8月5日 由晏就開始催淚彈放題放到夜晚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n殘留喺空氣嘅有毒氣體一定要長時間先散得晒 話唔定到宜家仲殘留緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時connect埋啲環保團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知班撐警師奶知道咗自己啲細路bb仔日日吸緊有毒氣體有機會變弱智會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文宣好唔好喺呢方面發展？<br />\n<br />\n咁可以connect埋班唔關心政治嘅怪獸家長港豬？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98873526cf54313f957a89b8674cf9894ce18f68","tid":1433442,"uid":21002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"轉去babycomdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2605b39bd18108b7a7346766050b2805e964685e","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"一齊去多啲狗宿舍 俾下催淚彈狗仔狗女聞下 毒氣應該由細聞到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f01ac227f88fb51dfea4f007392e640e3858357","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"有毒化學氣體係會殘留喺窗邊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記得洗乾淨窗邊窗簾呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7158cfe4c58a7137b324e218951f488be870f74","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"綠色和平：<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈爆發期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">開冷氣可能會帶嚟反效果。</span><br />\n有毒化學物質有可能<span style=\"color: red;\">被扯入冷氣或通風系統，之後吹出的風都有可能有殘留催淚煙</span><br />\n催淚彈含有有毒成份，對環境同人體都會帶嚟潛在嘅影響，綠色和平而家正就相關問題做資料搜集，有更詳細嘅資料會再公佈。<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"6ac2b4ef7c7a6d20a1ebad14874bb3e0cf747f6d","tid":1433442,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3135adf1a379020ff88acc5ff8cc5eb7f622a1","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"夏天咁熱 我諗狗宿舍個個都大個冷氣㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲請狗嫂狗仔狗女佢地喺屋企都慢慢吸有毒氣體啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd9919800da5b5b6b795b9490d44095696f1b4b","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ac2b4ef7c7a6d20a1ebad14874bb3e0cf747f6d","tid":1433442,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fcd9cbc4870aba79eb54829931b1cca3490aaa","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"班狗智商已經低㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗仔女 我諗都天資有限 宜家日日聞著催淚彈 唔知會唔會真係弱智㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9987d334a90190389132756114fd047e85f0c3eb","tid":1433442,"uid":41576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"一齊去多啲狗宿舍 探下班狗仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6f5eed46f2325edeb0cd74e606d77bc23cb183","tid":1433442,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"為藍絲長輩而設既Youtube頻道正式面世！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431722\" data-auto-link ta